script:
This is a Tier 4 alert for the Dubai metropolitan area. Automated shipping manifests are being flagged. Logistics networks under review. Citizens advised to monitor official updates.

In death, I see the patterns. Brain matter spatters prophecy.
shipping networks fail - another crack in democracy's skull.
My wound never healed. Neither will yours.
The theatre box drips eternal warnings.
Sic semper tyrannis. Always.
